Step 1: Turn on 8051 Trainer Kit
Step 2: Enter Assembler Using A
Step 3: Enter Program Starting From Address 4100H

For Anticlockwise Rotation:-
Step 4: Enter Values 0A, 05, 06, 09 at Memory Locations 4200H - 4203H using SD
Step 5: Execute Program using GO 4100
Step 6: Verify Rotation of Stepper Motor

For Clockwise Rotation:-
Step 4: Enter 09, 06, 05, 0A at Memory Locations 4200H - 4203H using SD
Step 5: Execute Program using GO 4100
Step 6: Verify Rotation of Stepper Motor